name: A Comic Strip about pretending as if the world is just okay
description:
Everything is happening at once, people are being born and dying, people are creating and destroying. And no matter how many people convince you that the world is ugly, evil,hateful, peace, it's love and mercy, it will exactly as it is.

It will exist as contradiction, life and death. The world is nature, and nature is the world. And we live in one big earth. 

And that's how it's going to be probably for the rest of our existence.

So we might as well just appreciate it as it is.
